                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; names of the donors; incipit of Text I; incipit of the prayers to be read; directives to the ministers; word yǝbärǝkǝwwo (fols. 3v-4v) and its two first letters; words säbbuḥni (fols. 3v-4r), lä-ʾǝgziʾabǝḥer (fols. 4v-5r) and their abbreviations; sentence nǝsebbǝḥakä ʾǝgziʾo and its abbreviation (fols. 24v-29r); words yǝtʾakkwät, its two first letters and its abbreviation (fols. 31r-31v); elements of the punctuation signs; Ethiopic numerals.</rubric>
